functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: What are the 5 countries with the highest reported cases of COVID-19 and when did the outbreak begin in each of these countries?
What are the 5 countries with the highest reported cases of COVID-19 and when did the outbreak begin in each of these countries?

Here are the 5 countries with the highest reported cases of COVID-19, as well as the date of the first reported case in each country:

1. United States: First case reported on January 20, 2020.
2. India: First case reported on January 30, 2020.
3. France: First case confirmed on January 24, 2020.
4. Brazil: The first case was confirmed on February 26, 2020.
5. Germany: The first case appeared on January 27, 2020.

Note that these statistics are dynamic and may change over time. This information is current as of January 2024.

Would you like to know more about the COVID-19 pandemic in these countries?
